item.title: FAQ
item.description: Questions What’s CAEOS? I thought this project was named Coner? CAEOS stands for “Coner is Autocross Event Operations Software”. There was already a user with the name Coner on GitHub, so an alternative was necessary. This will do! When can I run my autocross with Coner? Coner is a labor of love by its lead developer, but it does not pay his bills, nor does he wish that it would.

item.title: Contributing
item.description: Coner is a free, open source software project built by people who want to use it. We would love to have your help! Software development Features Bug fixes Technical improvements Code review Testing Bug reports User experience feedback Documentation If you want to help out, please get in touch!
